Class PageSliderIndicator.IndicatorSelectionHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.agp.database.Publisher<PageSlider.PageChangedListener>
      • ohos.agp.components.PageSliderIndicator.IndicatorSelectionHandler
  • Enclosing class:
    PageSliderIndicator

    protected static class PageSliderIndicator.IndicatorSelectionHandler
extends Publisher<PageSlider.PageChangedListener>
    Processes events of selecting a page contained in the PageSlider instance.

    This class is used to listen for and process events on page selection changes in PageSlider, so as to update the display of the indicator represented by PageSliderIndicator that is associated with PageSlider.
